INSTALLATION GUIDE FOR THE NG/AMS SOFTWARE PACKAGE:

        J.Knudstrup.

The steps needed for installing an NG/AMS system are described in the 
user's  manual provided for NG/AMS. To avoid redundant information, and 
maybe inconsistent information, please refer to this document.

The document can be retrieved from the NGAST home page:

	http://www.eso.org/projects/ngas

Specific information for ESO:

	http://www.eso.org/~jknudstr/NGAS/RELEASES/CURRENT/INSTALL

In addition it can be requested from the NGAS responsibles by sending
an email to the following email address:

	ngast@eso.org

Other questions or doubts in connection with the installation and 
configuration of NG/AMS should also be directed to this email address.

